<%- layout(`Boilerplate/boilerplate`) %>

<link
  rel="stylesheet"
  href="/Stylesheets/TESTIMONIALS/testimonials-styles.css"
/>

<div class="testimonials-container">
  <!-- NAV HELPER -->
  <div class="nav-helper"></div>
  <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
  <div class="hero d-g">
    <div class="hero-title">
      <h3 class="bold-text">
        CLIENT <span class="text-title-color">TESTIMONIALS</span>
      </h3>
      <p>
        We make decisions based on real data, ensuring your campaigns are
        optimized for maximum impact. And that's not all. We're constantly
        innovating and expanding our client portfolio. We start by getting to
        know your business inside and out. Through in-depth discussions and
        market research, we uncover your unique goals, target audience, and
        competition.
      </p>
      <a href="/become-client" class="get-started-btn-sm text-white"
        >Get Started</a
      >
    </div>
    <div class="hero-video">
      <video autoplay muted playsinline controls>
        <source
          src="https://crativesquad-blog-thumbnail.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/1725824557784-Testimonial+Final+Video.mp4"
          type="video/mp4"
        />
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
      </video>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="results-container">
    <div class="context" style="position: sticky; top: 20px">
      <h6 class="title-for-results bold-text text-title-size">
        <span class="title-for-results-span text-title-color"
          >BUILDING BRANDS</span
        >
        <br />
        WORLDWIDE
      </h6>
      <p class="contextForResults mt-4">
        We don't just talk strategy – we deliver real results, proven by the
        success stories of our amazing clients. We take pride in building
        long-term partnerships and tailoring our strategies to each client's
        unique goals. We understand the unique needs and landscape of the
        Canadian market, giving you a strategic edge.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="cards-container d-f">
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/icons/bishop-landing.svg"
          alt="..."
        />
        <h6 class="SM-font-size bold-text">STRATEGIC INFLUENCER MARKETING</h6>
        <p>
          Harness the power of influencers to connect with your target audience
          and expand your brand reach.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/icons/start-landing.svg"
          alt="..."
        />
        <h6 class="SM-font-size bold-text">ORGANIC SOCIAL MEDIA STRATEGY</h6>
        <p>
          Develop an organic SMM strategy that fosters genuine connections and
          drives engagement on social media platforms.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/icons/video-landing.svg"
          alt="..."
        />
        <h6 class="SM-font-size bold-text">
          IMPACTFUL CONTENT PROMOTION STRATEGIES
        </h6>
        <p>
          Craft a targeted content promotion strategy to amplify your content
          and ensure it reaches the right audience.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <img
          src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/icons/dollar-landing.svg"
          alt="..."
        />
        <h6 class="SM-font-size bold-text">DATA-DRIVEN PAID ADS</h6>
        <p>
          Leverage data insights to develop paid advertising campaigns that
          deliver measurable results and reach your ideal customers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

