    </div>
    <div class="about-us-main">
      <div class="about-us-card text-center" style="margin-bottom: 15px">
        <img src="https://www.creativesquad.ca/images/shared.svg" alt="..." />
        <h3 class="bold-text">STRATEGIC PLANNING & ROADMAP</h3>
        <p>
          Equipped with a clear understanding of your needs, we develop a
